# Bulak, Kizhinginsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Bulak (; , Bulag) is a rural locality (an ulus) in Kizhinginsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 202 as of 2010. There are 3 streets.
Geography
Bulak is located 56&nbsp;km northeast of Kizhinga (the district's administrative centre) by road. Chesan is the nearest rural locality.
